.TH FAUSTUS 1 "January 2026" "faustus" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
faustus \- TUI for managing Claude Code sessions
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B faustus
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B faustus
is a terminal user interface for browsing, searching, and managing Claude Code conversation sessions.
.PP
Sessions are stored in ~/.claude/projects/. Deleted sessions are moved to ~/.claude/faustus-trash/ and can be restored.
.SH KEYBINDINGS
.TP
.B j/k
Navigate down/up (or scroll preview when focused)
.TP
.B h/l
Switch tabs (Sessions / Bin)
.TP
.B gg/G
Jump to top/bottom
.TP
.B Ctrl+u/Ctrl+d
Half page up/down
.TP
.B /
Filter session list (or search in preview when focused)
.TP
.B s
Deep search across all session content
.TP
.B n/N
Next/previous search match
.TP
.B p
Toggle preview pane
.TP
.B Tab
Switch focus between list and preview
.TP
.B d
Delete (move to bin)
.TP
.B u
Restore from bin
.TP
.B c
Change name (rename session)
.TP
.B r
Reassign folder (single session)
.TP
.B R
Reassign folder (all matching sessions)
.TP
.B D
Clear bin (permanent delete)
.TP
.B ?
Toggle help
.TP
.B q
Quit
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.claude/projects/
Claude Code session storage
.TP
.I ~/.claude/faustus-trash/
Deleted sessions (recoverable)
